{
  "store-new-launch": {
    "header": {
      "title": "🏬 New Store Alert!"
    },
    "body": {
      "content": "# Welcome {{storeName}} 🎉\n\nA brand new store has joined BuyConn!\n\n### Store Details:\n- 🏷️ **Category**: {{storeCategory}}\n- 📍 **Location**: {{storeLocation}}\n- 🌟 **Rating**: {{storeRating}}/5\n\n*Discover amazing deals today!*",
      "type": "markdown",
      "image": {
        "uri": "{{storeImageUrl}}",
        "alt": "{{storeName}} store preview"
      }
    },
    "footer": {
      "visitStore": {
        "text": "🛍️ Visit Store",
        "type": "navigation",
        "action": "open_store",
        "actionType": "open_store",
        "actionData": {
          "url": "buyconn://stores/{{storeId}}"
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "store-new-offer": {
    "header": { "title": "🏬 New Store Offer!" },
    "body": {
      "content": "# Fresh Deals 🎉\n\n{{storeName}} has a new offer waiting for you!\n\n### Offer:\n- 🛒 **Discount**: {{discountPercent}}%\n- 📅 **Valid Till**: {{offerEndDate}}",
      "type": "markdown",
      "image": {
        "uri": "{{storeImageUrl}}",
        "alt": "{{storeName}} offer preview"
      }
    },
    "footer": {
      "viewStore": {
        "text": "🛍️ View Store",
        "type": "navigation",
        "action": "open_store",
        "actionType": "deep_link",
        "actionData": { "url": "buyconn://store/{{storeId}}" }
      }
    }
  },
  "store-special-offer": {
    "header": {
      "title": "🔥 Hot Offer from {{storeName}}!"
    },
    "body": {
      "content": "# Special Deal 💥\n\n{{storeName}} just launched a new offer.\n\n### Offer:\n- 🛒 **Discount**: {{discountPercent}}%\n- ⏰ **Valid Until**: {{offerEndDate}}\n- 📍 **Store**: {{storeName}}\n\n*Don’t miss this limited-time deal!*",
      "type": "markdown",
      "image": {
        "uri": "{{storeOfferImageUrl}}",
        "alt": "{{storeName}} offer banner"
      }
    },
    "footer": {
      "shopNow": {
        "text": "🛒 Shop Now",
        "type": "navigation",
        "action": "open_store_offer",
        "actionType": "open_store",
        "actionData": {
          "url": "buyconn://stores/{{storeId}}/offers"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
